content_vision: The man is dark and quiet, but when he finds his guitar, he gets all his thoughts out by playing. He has a guitar soul. The only thing that matters in the moment is when he hears his own voice through the guitar.

true religions so distressed, they just hangin' on me,

and skwab, don't let fame get to your head
you should have never gone to hollywood, now you're wishing you were dead.

Chorus 2:
i'm way too focused, can't afford to slip,
we regulated, can't afford to trip.
i'm all revved up, ready to go,
you know i'm a father, gotta put on a show.

Verse 3:
gonna pour another drink and throw it back,
forget all my problems, just let go of the past.
i got that vibe, that's what she choosin',
ridin' in the cadillac, that's how we cruisin'.
got no time to stop and fix my nails,
got places to go, people to see, no fails,
i'm a carnivore, tearing through the night,
won't let anyone dim my shine or put up a fight.

Chorus 3:
maybe it was just too much, had to say it again,
oh amen, who is it, what they tryna pretend?
brooklyn zoo, all we got is slugs, that's all we feed,
and a black mustache, that's just how we breed.

Bridge:
you strut around so uneasy, can't deny it,
you ain't showing no love, just cold and heartless,
but this bruh still stole the win, nothin' to hide.
i've reached the top, got everything i desire,

active_struct.name: The Musical Journey
attrs: has a strong intro that immediately draws the listener in
features pre-chorus and chorus repetitions which creates a catchy and sing-along quality to the song
includes a bridge which adds variety to the song and may add emotional depth or intensity
allows for multiple verse-chorus repetitions, making it suitable for a longer song
ends with a final chorus which ties the song together and leaves a lasting impression

struct_suggs.name: The Musical Journey
attrs: has a strong intro that immediately draws the listener in
features pre-chorus and chorus repetitions which creates a catchy and sing-along quality to the song
includes a bridge which adds variety to the song and may add emotional depth or intensity
allows for multiple verse-chorus repetitions, making it suitable for a longer song
ends with a final chorus which ties the song together and leaves a lasting impression

struct_suggs.name: The Chorus Chaser
attrs: has a distinct and memorable intro
utilizes two pre-choruses which can help build tension and excitement leading up to the chorus
includes a bridge after the second chorus which can add a new layer to the song or change the mood/tone
ends with a final chorus which can create a sense of resolution or closure
allows for flexibility in switching between pre-chorus and chorus order (ex. PC1, C1, PC2, C2 or PC1, PC2, C1, C2)

struct_suggs.name: Soulful Strings
attrs: has a strong and attention-grabbing intro
features an instrumental break after the second chorus which can showcase a talented musician or add a dynamic element to the song
allows for multiple verse-chorus repetitions, making it suitable for a longer song
includes a distinct bridge which may change up the melody or rhythm of the song
ends with a final chorus, tying the song together and leaving a lasting impact on the listener

struct_suggs.name: A Melodic Adventure
attrs: has a unique and attention-grabbing intro featuring a solo or instrumental theme melody
utilizes two verses and pre-choruses before the first chorus, which can create a sense of buildup or anticipation
includes a bridge after the second chorus which adds variation to the song
ends with a final chorus, providing a sense of closure and bringing the song full circle

struct_suggs.name: The Rising Rhythm
attrs: has a strong and catchy intro
starts with a pre-chorus before the first verse, building anticipation for the chorus
includes a bridge before the final chorus, adding a new layer to the song and increasing emotional intensity
ends with a final chorus, providing a satisfying conclusion to the song
allows for flexibility in switching between pre-chorus and chorus order (ex. PC1, C1, PC2, C2 or PC1, PC2, C1, C2)

struct_suggs.name: Instrumental Inspiration
attrs: has a unique and attention-grabbing intro
features an instrumental break after the first verse which can showcase a talented musician or add a dynamic element to the song
includes two pre-choruses, creating a sense of buildup leading to the first chorus
utilizes a bridge after the second chorus, adding variation and keeping the song interesting
ends with a final chorus, providing a strong sense of closure and leaving an impression on the listener

struct_suggs.name: The Musical Masterpiece
attrs: has a strong and engaging intro
features two distinct choruses with a pre-chorus in between, creating a sense of anticipation and buildup
utilizes a bridge after the third chorus, adding a new layer to the song
includes an instrumental break before the final chorus, showcasing a musician or adding a dynamic element
ends with a final chorus, bringing the song to a satisfying conclusion

struct_suggs.name: Instrumental Interlude
attrs: has a distinct and attention-grabbing intro
starts with a pre-chorus before the first verse, building anticipation for the chorus
includes an instrumental break before the second verse, showcasing a musician or adding a dynamic element
features two pre-choruses, creating a sense of buildup leading to the first chorus
ends with a final chorus, providing a strong sense of closure and impactful ending to the song

struct_suggs.name: The Instrumental Showdown
attrs: has a strong and memorable intro
features an instrumental solo after the second chorus, showcasing a musician and adding a dynamic element to the song
includes a bridge before the third chorus, adding a new layer to the song and changing up the mood or tempo
utilizes two instrumental sections, allowing for further showcase of musical talent or variation in melody/rhythm
ends with an outro, providing a unique and impactful ending to the song

struct_suggs.name: Guitar Groove
attrs: has a catchy and memorable intro
features an instrumental break before the first verse, showcasing a musician and adding a dynamic element to the song
utilizes a bridge after the second chorus, adding a new layer and keeping the song interesting
includes a solo before the third chorus, showcasing a musician and adding a dynamic element
ends with an outro, providing a unique and impactful ending to the song
